Library Management System

Development Environment
  - front-end: Angular 
  - back-end: Express
  - DB: MongoDB
  - check `env` folder for more detail

Basic Function
  - Book
    . search book
    . view book detail
    . edit book
    . delete book
  - Transaction
    . borrow book
    . return book
  - Account
    . signup
    . signin
    . logout
    . check profile
